---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About PlateDrop - Your Home Gym Deal Finder"
  description="Learn about PlateDrop's mission to help fitness enthusiasts find the best deals on quality home gym equipment. Daily curated deals, expert reviews, and honest recommendations."
>
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-primary text-white py-20 md:py-16">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10" style="background: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='0.05'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E&quot;);"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-[800px] mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6 text-white leading-tight">Building Your Dream Home Gym, One Deal at a Time</h1>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed opacity-95 max-w-[60ch] mx-auto">
          We're on a mission to make quality fitness equipment accessible to everyone through smart deal hunting and honest recommendations.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="py-20 bg-bg">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-primary rounded-2xl text-white">
            <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            Home gym equipment shouldn't break the bank. We track prices across major retailers daily,
            finding genuine deals on quality equipment so you can build your dream gym without overspending.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-primary rounded-2xl text-white">
            <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M9 11l3 3L22 4"></path>
              <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Quality First</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            Not all deals are created equal. We focus on reputable brands and retailers, ensuring every
            deal we feature represents genuine value and quality equipment that will last.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-primary rounded-2xl text-white">
            <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
              <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Daily Updates</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            Prices change constantly. Our automated system checks deals every day, ensuring you never
            miss out on limited-time offers or price drops on equipment you've been eyeing.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-bg-secondary">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-[70ch] mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">How PlateDrop Started</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 text-text-secondary">
          Like many fitness enthusiasts, we started building a home gym during the pandemic. What should
          have been exciting quickly became frustrating‚Äîprices were inflated, stock was limited, and
          finding genuine deals felt impossible.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 text-text-secondary">
          We spent hours comparing prices across different retailers, tracking price histories, and
          waiting for the right moment to buy. That's when we realized: there had to be a better way.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 text-text-secondary">
          PlateDrop was born from that frustration. We built a system that does the heavy lifting‚Äîtracking
          prices, validating deals, and curating the best offers daily. Now, instead of spending hours
          hunting for deals, you can spend that time actually working out.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">What We Stand For</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="card p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-primary">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">üéØ Transparency</h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            We're upfront about our retailer partnerships and maintain honest
            recommendations. If it's not a good deal, we won't feature it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-primary">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">üìä Data-Driven</h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            Every deal is validated against historical pricing data. We show you real savings,
            not inflated "discounts" from artificial list prices.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-primary">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">ü§ù Community-Focused</h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            We're building this for the home gym community. Your feedback shapes our features,
            and your success stories inspire us to keep improving.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-primary">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">üîí Privacy-Respecting</h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            No tracking pixels, no data selling, no creepy retargeting. Just honest deal curation
            and helpful content.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-bg-secondary">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Retailers We Track</h2>
      <p class="text-center text-lg text-text-secondary mb-12 max-w-[60ch] mx-auto">
        We monitor prices across the most trusted names in fitness equipment
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 max-w-[900px] mx-auto">
        <div class="card p-4 px-6 text-center font-semibold text-base transition-all duration-300 hover:border-primary hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">Rogue Fitness</div>
        <div class="card p-4 px-6 text-center font-semibold text-base transition-all duration-300 hover:border-primary hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">REP Fitness</div>
        <div class="card p-4 px-6 text-center font-semibold text-base transition-all duration-300 hover:border-primary hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">Amazon</div>
        <div class="card p-4 px-6 text-center font-semibold text-base transition-all duration-300 hover:border-primary hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">Titan Fitness</div>
        <div class="card p-4 px-6 text-center font-semibold text-base transition-all duration-300 hover:border-primary hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">PowerBlock</div>
        <div class="card p-4 px-6 text-center font-semibold text-base transition-all duration-300 hover:border-primary hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">Bowflex</div>
        <div class="card p-4 px-6 text-center font-semibold text-base transition-all duration-300 hover:border-primary hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">CAP Barbell</div>
        <div class="card p-4 px-6 text-center font-semibold text-base transition-all duration-300 hover:border-primary hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">Yes4All</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-[600px] mx-auto text-center p-12 bg-gradient-primary rounded-2xl text-white">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Start Saving Today</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6 opacity-95 text-white">
          Check out today's deals and see how much you can save on your home gym equipment.
        </p>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4">View Today's Deals</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
